desc: C_ApplyMaintResp? is a on/off switch for applying the maintenance respiration; for a default value of 0 all the rest is ignored

C_RelRespCurrHarv is the relative weighting factor for developing fruits as part of total biomass as used for maintenance respiration

desc: C_RespPerBiomass is the relative use of resources for maintenance respiration per unit biomass
C_RespTemp is a graphical relation between temperature and maintenance respiration
